    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-strung S54B32 engine, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for exceptional throttle response. This example has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement, ensuring the structural and internal integrity of the chassis and rotating assembly. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers crisp engagement, transferring power to the rear wheels via the M Variable Differential Lock. Suspension geometry is preserved with refreshed bushings, maintaining the precise handling characteristics this platform is known for. A true driver's car with a healthy compression profile and linear power delivery.",
