      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved\u2014perfect for someone looking for a reliable ride that still looks great on the road. It runs smoothly and is totally ready for its next adventure with a new owner! I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
